  messages:
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: 'Hello! Welcome to Curling Valley! I''m Elwin, your guide. It''s great
      to see you! '
    GameEventTrigger: Happy
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: Are you ready to learn the secrets of curling?
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: 'Great! Curling is a precision and strategy sport played on ice. '
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: 'Each team tries to slide their stones to the target center, and the
      closer to the center, the higher the score. '
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: This game requires skill and teamwork, and it's a lot of fun!
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: 'Now, let''s start with the basics. First, you need to learn how to
      launch the curling stone. '
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: Follow me to the hack, and I'll show you how to properly hold and push
      the stone.
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: 'Pay attention to my posture and the force of the push. '
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: "Now it's your turn to try. Don\u2019t worry, I\u2019ll guide you through
      it."
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: "Very good! You\u2019ve got the hang of the basic launching technique. "
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: "Next, let\u2019s learn how to use the broom to control the stone\u2019s
      speed and direction."
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: 'Using the broom while the stone is sliding can help keep it on the
      right track and adjust the speed to reach the target. '
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: Try controlling the broom to see if you can stop the stone at the target
      location.
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: "Fantastic! It looks like you\u2019ve got the basics of curling down. "
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: 'Remember, this game is not just about skill but also strategy and teamwork. '
    GameEventTrigger: 
  - title: Elwin
    image: {fileID: 0}
    message: Ready to join a real match and compete against other players?
